MOST IMMEDIATE
No. 1/34/1/2009-Cab.
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 14h June, 2009
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 14 June, 2009:-
The Prime Minister relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of
Water Resources;
(i)
(ii)
Shri Pawan Kumar Bansal assumed the charge of the office of the
Minister of Water Resources. He will continue to hold the charge of the
office of the Minister of Parliamentary Affairs;
Shri Arun Yadav relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of
State in the Ministry of Youth Affairs and Sports and assumed charge of
the office of the Minister of State in the Ministry of Heavy Industries and
Public Enterprises;
(ii)
Shri Pratik Prakashbapu Patil relinquished the charge of the office of the
Minister of State in the Ministry of Heavy Industries and Public Enterprises
and assumed charge of the office of the Minister of State in the Ministry of
Youth Affairs and Sports.
(iv)
Qualoli
